{"tid":1898330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣要正視聽：攞返自己嘅錢有咩問題？","createTime":"2020-02-26T04:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T05:17:40.000Z","uid":194069,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8eaeef65ea43e48645c1c2e34f30cc80e6f1ff52","tid":1898330,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"選舉近了<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3DAA9kC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DAA9kC.jpg&h=aeff60bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家記得要用錢振興黃色經濟圈同支持手足<br />\n幫大家回顧下呢個政權9個月以後點對你？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXqxshM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXqxshM.jpg&h=bd1a05b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/teCjRKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FteCjRKs.jpg&h=83de17ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FwnzFCO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFwnzFCO.jpg&h=72aa5f46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akxTbKt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakxTbKt.jpg&h=e6b8302b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2irwKu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2irwKu.jpg&h=5785f607&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jBum44v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjBum44v.jpg&h=89d6c3da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K4EaYpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4EaYpw.jpg&h=b65280bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HG9N0CS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHG9N0CS.jpg&h=be5bbd4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjOrwKx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjOrwKx.jpg&h=3dee5b88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJbdbKy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJbdbKy.jpg&h=c7c3e0bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下仲有啲野想講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢除功能組別 不要進攻<br />\n全面落實雙普選</span></span><br />\n冇普選下落實嘅其他訴求都係假 因為<span style=\"color: red;\">冇民意授權</span>嘅所有制度同措施都係不公義 係777/親共特首成立嘅獨立調查委員會只會係<span style=\"color: red;\">自己人查自己人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong>美國民主人權法</strong></strong></span></span>入面有提<span style=\"color: red;\">會將香港普選納入評核範圍內香港普選 </span><br />\n成日話人權法冇用<br />\n只不過大家睇唔到佢已經發揮緊箇中功效啫<br />\n就好似<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><strong>黑警將街頭抗爭對眼球嘅衝擊轉移到去被自殺、被跳樓、浮屍等冇可疑事件之上</strong></strong></span></span><br />\n但其實係有更大嘅殺傷力<br />\n再者 人權法可以起<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">警世之效</span></span><br />\n睇下當時法案過咗之後其他西方國家都開始出現一啲反共嘅措施<br />\n我地更加要借力打力，襯全球反共氣氛高漲時拉自己一把<br />\n如果唔好好利用<br />\n武漢肺炎後就會變到當年剛經歷完沙士嘅香港咁<br />\n經濟重創後成立<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自由行、CEPA(內地與香港關於建立更緊密經貿關係的安排)</span></span>等措施黎「救港」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>實際係乘機箝制香港、加速染紅</strong></span></span><br />\n依家呢個k型，向大陸人獻媚嘅經濟結構都係拜當年嘅措施所賜，大家切記唔好咁短視！<br />\n共產黨一貫主張以虛無主義去集權<br />\n消滅哂現有嘅制度、社會秩序、道德價值等黎「破舊立新」<br />\nE.g. 納粹、文革、土改、三反五反blablabla<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以 疫症過後我地抗爭嘅目標應直指全面普選，所有遊行集會、街頭抗爭、國際線都以呢個目標爭取係9月前/延期全面普選立法會、廢除功能組別！<br />\n仲要抵制所有同中共有關嘅「援助」</span></span></strong><br />\n最後祝大家<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">身體健康，光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"98ae1991390efb3648228e036f0628fce932d644","tid":1898330,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:58:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ededc21839b9780fd20dd7c33e57df9600273ed","tid":1898330,"uid":194069,"like":0,